∀syscall_number S: filter_action(S) ∈ {SECCOMP_RET_KILL_PROCESS, SECCOMP_RET_KILL_THREAD, SECCOMP_RET_TRAP, SECCOMP_RET_ERRNO, SECCOMP_RET_TRACE, SECCOMP_RET_LOG, SECCOMP_RET_ALLOW}
∧ default_action(S) ∈ {KILL, ERRNO} when no rule matches
Filter must be total: every possible syscall has a defined action, even if the action is the default.
